{"tid":2017730,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡雅文法官:於我而言 612立法會公眾入口衝擊事件比2016亞皆老街情況更為嚴重","createTime":"2020-05-15T08:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T01:45:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":259,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"863f23eb95cb413686b1b1c355a6fa4a5ab5cd46","tid":2017730,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/DCCC000783_2019.docx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Fdoc%2Fjudg%2Fword%2Fvetted%2Fother%2Fen%2F2019%2FDCCC000783_2019.docx&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=3aa62e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/doc/judg/word/vetted/other/en/2019/DCCC000783_2019.docx</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Court of Appeal in Leung Tin Kei set out various factors to be taken into account when passing sentence on the offence of riot. Courts must consider these factors and principles to arrive at a sentence according to the facts of each individual case. In that authority, the Court of Appeal upheld the sentences imposed. Those factors include:-<br />\n<br />\n(1) whether the riot was spontaneous or premeditated; if it was the latter, how detailed and precise the plan was;<br />\n<br />\n(2) the number of people engaged in the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(3) the degree of violence used by the rioters, including whether weapons were used and, if so, what kind and quantity of weapons;<br />\n<br />\n(4) the scale of the riot, including the time, location, the number of places and the area in which the riot took place;<br />\n<br />\n(5) the duration of the riot, including whether the riot was prolonged, and whether it still went on despite repeated warnings by the police or public officers;<br />\n<br />\n(6) the harm caused by the riot; for example, whether there was any loss or damage to properties and, if so, to what extent; whether anyone was injured and, if so, the number of injured persons and the degree of injury;<br />\n<br />\n(7) what imminence and gravity of threat was caused by the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(8) the nature and extent of nuisance caused to the public by the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(9) the impact on the relationship among community groups caused by the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(10) burden caused to public expenditure by the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(11) the offender&rsquo;s role and group participation; for instance, apart from taking part in the riot, whether he had arranged, led, summoned, incited or advocated others to take part in the riot;<br />\n<br />\n(12) whether the offender committed any other crimes during the course of the riot.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">In Leung Tin Kei&rsquo;s case the riot took place on 9 February 2016 in Argyle Street. Although I have not seen any video footage of that riot, I read a description of the events set out in the reasons for sentence. In my view, this riot in the public entrance of the Legislature is more serious than the riot on Argyle Street.</span></strong>"},{"pid":"629de1d24bd08133536879f718bae1f1565ace9d","tid":2017730,"uid":253978,"like":90,"dislike":16,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Although I have not seen any video footage of that riot,</span></span>"},{"pid":"3cc4ab4506b622f1a9c5a0eee07e6841c9c9c911","tid":2017730,"uid":41411,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:39:40.000Z","msg":"有幾嚴重呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"c21544c91397e34799cc92baee91832917a4d489","tid":2017730,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629de1d24bd08133536879f718bae1f1565ace9d","tid":2017730,"uid":253978,"like":90,"dislike":16,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Although I have not seen any video footage of that riot,</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ef28f115d8ebf61eb095c4e90aa4d3b067cf2","tid":2017730,"uid":134474,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W28VBgx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW28VBgx.gif&h=4659eae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n612火魔都冇"},{"pid":"2354ec371d72edc2547b6c05f0e4b2559811432d","tid":2017730,"uid":64337,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:41:30.000Z","msg":"依加問你個人感受?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8437a575bcd5083160426e13cf4769296d6ddd","tid":2017730,"uid":253978,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"梁天琦都坐6年<br />\n咁嚴重<br />\n告上高院<br />\n陪審團打救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e142615f313a265ae49c96c3009dc787c1c362","tid":2017730,"uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"c21544c91397e34799cc92baee91832917a4d489","tid":2017730,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629de1d24bd08133536879f718bae1f1565ace9d","tid":2017730,"uid":253978,"like":90,"dislike":16,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Although I have not seen any video footage of that riot,</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:41:49.000Z","msg":"八毛今次罕有地quote得幾好"},{"pid":"7fc920da40d8cee804f1ce844f3e36ce0650bb88","tid":2017730,"uid":24